Class SlidingWindow

  • java.lang.Object
    • weka.filters.Filter
      • weka.filters.SimpleFilter
        • weka.filters.SimpleBatchFilter
          • weka.filters.unsupervised.attribute.ProteinFilter
            • weka.filters.unsupervised.attribute.SlidingWindow
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, weka.core.CapabilitiesHandler, weka.core.CapabilitiesIgnorer, weka.core.CommandlineRunnable, weka.core.OptionHandler, weka.core.RevisionHandler

    public class SlidingWindow
extends ProteinFilter
    Counts the amino acids in a protein sequence. Optionally scales counts to unit sum.

    Valid options are: 

     -R <index>
  Sets the index of the string attribute.
 
     -S
  Scales counts to sum to unity.
